{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量小灯泡工作时的电阻。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><em>R=U/I</em></span></span></em><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">电源、开关、小灯泡、电流表、电压表、滑动变阻器、导线</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">将滑动变阻器滑片调到阻值最大处；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">闭合开关，记录电压表和电流表示数；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调节滑动变阻器滑片位置，使小灯泡微弱发光；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">记录电压表和电流表示数；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">5.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">调节滑动变阻器滑片位置，使小灯泡正常发光；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">6.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">记录电压表和电流表示数；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">7.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">计算小灯泡的电阻。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小灯泡亮度逐渐增加过程中电阻逐渐变大。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">小灯泡的电阻随温度的升高而增加。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}